trans-unit.source: Provides data for the **Navigating** event.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den **navigere** hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: These event arguments contain information about the navigation that was requested, and are passed to handlers of the **Navigating** event, which is implemented by the following: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> - <xref:System.Windows.Application.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> NavigatingCancelEventArgs encapsulates the following details of the navigation request: - **Navigation Initiation**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.NavigationMode%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Disse hendelsen argumentene inneholder informasjon om navigering som ble forespurt, og som er sendt til behandlingsprogrammer for den **navigere** som implementeres av følgende:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>- <xref:System.Windows.Application.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>NavigatingCancelEventArgs innkapsler følgende informasjon for forespørselen som navigasjon:- **navigasjon Start**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.NavigationMode%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator%2A> <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.NavigationMode%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Application.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Content**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Navigasjon innhold**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation Request**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Navigasjon forespørselen**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationFailedEventArgs.WebRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: - **Navigation State**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.TargetContentState%2A>.
trans-unit.target: - **Navigation State**: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.TargetContentState%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.TargetContentState%2A></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ContentStateToSave%2A></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.ExtraData%2A>

trans-unit.source: This information allows you to both evaluate the nature of the navigation request, and view and update specified request details before navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: Denne informasjonen kan du både evaluere typen navigeringsforespørselen, og Vis og Oppdater angitte Forespørselsdetaljer før navigering.

trans-unit.source: Based on the navigation request information provided by NavigatingCancelEventArgs, or based on application-specific state or code, you can completely prevent navigation by setting the <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property to `true` (by default, <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> is `false`).
trans-unit.target: Basert på navigasjon Forespørselsinformasjon leveres av NavigatingCancelEventArgs eller basert på programspesifikk tilstand eller kode, kan du fullstendig hindre navigasjon ved å angi den <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>egenskapen `true` (som standard <xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>er `false`).</xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs.Cancel%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to the content object that is being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Henter en referanse til innhold som navigeres til objektet.

trans-unit.source: You can navigate to content using either a [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] or an object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan gå til innhold ved hjelp av enten en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] eller et objekt.

trans-unit.source: When navigating to an object, which occurs when calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, Content contains a reference to the content object that is being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Når du navigerer til et objekt som oppstår når du kaller <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, innhold inneholder en referanse til innhold som navigeres til objektet.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A> property will be `null`.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>blir `null`.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Uri%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Object> reference to the content object that is being navigated to; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>referanse til innhold objektet som blir navigeres til; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"></xref> object that is associated with the back navigation history entry for the page being navigated from.
trans-unit.target: Får eller angir den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"> </xref> objektet som er forbundet med tilbake navigering historikkoppføringen for siden blir navigerer fra.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating> event is raised when navigating from one piece of content to another.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating>Denne hendelsen oppstår når navigere fra én del av innholdet til en annen.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigating>

trans-unit.source: The content that is being navigated from is added to back navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Innholdet i navigeres fra legges til igjen navigasjon historikk.

trans-unit.source: You can set ContentStateToSave with a custom <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object to associate state information with content in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Du kan konfigurere ContentStateToSave med en egendefinert <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objekt for å knytte statusinformasjon til innholdet i loggen for navigasjon.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"></xref> object that is associated with the back navigation history entry for the page being navigated from.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"> </xref> objektet som er forbundet med tilbake navigasjon historikkoppføringen for siden blir navigerer fra.

trans-unit.source: Gets the optional data <xref:System.Object> that was passed when navigation started.
trans-unit.target: Henter den valgfrie data <xref:System.Object>som ble sendt når navigasjon startet.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: ExtraData can be used to pass context-specific data that is specific to a particular navigation.
trans-unit.target: ExtraData kan brukes til å sende kontekstavhengige data som er spesifikk for et bestemt navigasjon.

trans-unit.source: ExtraData contains a reference to the object that is passed as the second argument when calling either <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: ExtraData inneholder en referanse til objektet som blir sendt som det andre argumentet når du kaller enten <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ikke, er det `null`.

trans-unit.source: The optional data <xref:System.Object> that was passed when navigation started.
trans-unit.target: Det valgfrie data <xref:System.Object>som ble sendt når navigasjon startet.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the navigator (<xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref>) that is specified by <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*> is servicing this navigation, or whether a parent navigator is doing so.
trans-unit.target: Angir om navigatoren (<xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref>) som er angitt i <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*>behandler denne navigasjonsruten, eller om et overordnet navigatoren gjør so.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Boolean> value that is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the navigator that is specified by <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*> is servicing this navigation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Boolean>verdi som <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> Hvis navigatoren som er angitt av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*>behandler denne navigasjon.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Navigator*> </xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> is returned, such as during a nested <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref> navigation.
trans-unit.target: Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> returneres, for eksempel som i løpet av en nestet <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref> navigeringen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode"></xref> value that indicates the type of navigation that is occurring.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode"> </xref> verdi som angir typen navigasjon pågår.

trans-unit.source: The types of navigation that can occur are: - Navigating to new content (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).
trans-unit.target: Typene for navigasjon som kan oppstå: – navigering til nytt innhold (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>

trans-unit.source: - Navigating to the previous item in back navigation history (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).
trans-unit.target: -Navigering til forrige element i tilbake navigering historikk (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>

trans-unit.source: - Navigating to the next item in forward navigation history (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).
trans-unit.target: -Navigere til neste element i Videresend navigasjon loggen (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>

trans-unit.source: - Refreshing existing content (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).
trans-unit.target: -Oppdateringen eksisterende innhold (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode"></xref> value that indicates the type of navigation that is occurring.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationMode"> </xref> verdi som angir hvilken type navigering som pågår.

trans-unit.source: The navigator that raised this event.
trans-unit.target: Navigatoren som var årsaken til denne hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: While Navigator stores a reference to the navigator that raised this event, the navigator may not have actually initiated the navigation.
trans-unit.target: Under navigatoren inneholder en referanse til navigatoren som var årsaken til denne hendelsen, kan navigatoren ikke ha faktisk startet navigeringen.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether this navigator did initiate the current navigation, inspect the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: For å fastslå om denne navigatoren starte gjeldende navigasjon undersøke den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.IsNavigationInitiator%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that is the navigator that raised this event
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>som navigatoren som starter hendelsen</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"></xref> object that is to be applied to the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"> </xref> objektet som skal brukes til innholdet i navigeres til.

trans-unit.source: TargetContentState will contain a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object if navigating to content in back or forward navigation history that has a <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object associated with it.
trans-unit.target: TargetContentState inneholder en <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objektet hvis navigering til innhold i tilbake eller videresende navigering historikk som har et <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objekt som er tilknyttet.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"></xref> object that is to be applied to the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState"> </xref> objektet som skal brukes til innholdet i navigeres til.

trans-unit.source: Gets the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Henter den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for innhold som navigeres til.

trans-unit.source: You can navigate to content using either an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] or an object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan gå til innhold ved hjelp av enten en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] eller et objekt.

trans-unit.source: When navigating to an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], which occurs when calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, Uri contains the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Under navigering til en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], som oppstår når du kaller <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, URIen inneholder den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] på innholdet som navigeres til.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A> property will be `null`.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A>blir `null`.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigatingCancelEventArgs.Content%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Uri> for the content being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Uri>for innhold som navigeres til.</xref:System.Uri>

trans-unit.source: If navigating to an object, Uri is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du navigerer til et objekt, URIen er <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> object that is used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>objekt som brukes til å be om det angitte innholdet.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> is an abstract base class that encapsulates a Web request, and is protocol agnostic.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>er en abstrakt basisklasse som innkapsler en forespørsel, og er likegyldig til protokollen.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For each common protocol, the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] includes a class that derives from <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> and extends it with protocol specific state and behavior, including: - <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `pack://` scheme to request application data files (see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).
trans-unit.target: For hver vanlige protokoll den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_titlewinfx](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-titlewinfx-md.md)] inkluderer en klasse som er avledet fra <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>og utvider med bestemte status for protokollen og virkemåten, inkludert:- <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] som bruker den `pack://` skjemaet til å be om programmet datafiler (se [WPF programmet ressursen, innhold og datafiler](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackWebRequest> </xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `http://` scheme to request files from Web servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] som bruker den `http://` fargevalg forespørselen filene fra nettservere.</xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `ftp://` scheme to request files from FTP servers.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] som bruker den `ftp://` skjemaet forespørselen filene fra FTP-servere.</xref:System.Net.FtpWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] that use the `file://` scheme to request local files.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-urisharpplural-md.md)] som bruker den `file://` skjemaet til å be om lokale filer.</xref:System.Net.FileWebRequest>

trans-unit.source: You can both view and modify <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> details.
trans-unit.target: Du kan både vise og endre <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>detaljer.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: WebRequest is `null` when navigation occurs by: - Using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> control.
trans-unit.target: WebRequest er `null` når navigering av: – med den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>

trans-unit.source: - Calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A> - Setting <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: -Kaller <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>- innstillingen <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Content%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Navigating through HTML content in a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.
trans-unit.target: -Navigering i HTML-innhold i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> object that is used to request the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref:System.Net.WebRequest?displayProperty=fullName> objekt som brukes til å be om det angitte innholdet.
